src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F126482149.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20trailer%20for%20Rani%20Mukerji's%20'Mardaani%203'%20has%20been%20released.%20Mukerji%20returns%20as%20cop%20Shivani%20Shivaji%20Roy%20investigating%20missing%20children.%20Mallika%20Prasad%20plays%20the%20formidable%20villain%20Amma.%20The%20film%20is%20directed%20by%20Abhiraj%20Minawala.%20'Mardaani%203'%20is%20scheduled%20for%20release%20on%20January%2030.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20CEO%20who%20built%20a%20fantasy%20board%20of%20directors%20with%20AI%20versions%20of%20leaders%20like%20Steve%20Jobs%20and%20Warren%20Buffett%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22723%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696168c164858d02d2181a7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Blumberg%20built%20an%20AI%20agent%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20fantasy%20board%20of%20directors%3Cp%3EMarkup%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMatt%20Blumberg%2C%20a%20serial%20tech%20CEO%2C%20created%20an%20AI%20agent%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20dream%20board%20of%20directors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20board%20is%20like%20a%20fantasy%20football%20team%20comprising%20famous%20business%20leaders%2C%20past%20and%20present.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBlumberg%20said%20his%20agent%20is%20a%20great%20thought%20partner%2C%20though%20it%20lacks%20real-world%20context%20and%20human%20cues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Matt%20Blumberg%2C%20a%20four-time%20technology%20CEO%20who%20now%20leads%20Markup%20AI%2C%20maker%20of%20an%20AI%20platform%20designed%20to%20help%20brands%20safely%20scale%20AI-generated%20content.%20He%20is%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20run%20an%20AI%20company%2C%20I%20try%20to%20build%20AI%20agents%20and%20use%20AI%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can.%20In%20October%2C%20I%20got%20an%20idea%20to%20build%20what%20I%20call%20a%20fantasy%20board%20of%20directors%20from%20another%20CEO%2C%20and%20with%20his%20permission%2C%20I%20made%20a%20version%20of%20my%20own%20to%20use%20as%20a%20personal%20thought%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20actual%20human%20board%2C%20and%20it's%20fantastic.%20I%20get%20really%20good%20advice%20from%20them.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20create%20a%20fantasy%20board%20because%20mine%20is%20limited%20by%20the%20five%20people%20who%20are%20on%20it%20and%20the%20experiences%20that%20they%20have%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20first%20thing%20my%20executive%20team%20and%20I%20did%20was%20create%20a%20fantasy%20draft.%20It's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20play%20on%20fantasy%20football%20and%20fantasy%20basketball.%20But%20instead%20of%20it%20being%20a%20competitive%20thing%2C%20where%20each%20of%20us%20would%20draft%20our%20own%20teams%2C%20we%20drafted%20just%20one%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20by%20making%20a%20spreadsheet%20of%20essentially%20famous%20people%2C%20largely%20but%20not%20entirely%2C%20from%20the%20business%20world.%20We%20divided%20them%20into%20categories%2C%20including%20iconic%20business%20leaders%2C%20tech%20CEOs%2C%20VCs%2C%20authors%2C%20and%20thought%20leaders.%20We%20also%20had%20a%20category%20for%20different%20voices%2C%20such%20as%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20and%20Taylor%20Swift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20had%20something%20like%20a%20draft%20where%20we%20picked%20a%20couple%20of%20people%20from%20each%20category%20that%20we%20wanted%20on%20the%20board.%20We%20settled%20on%20about%2015%20names%2C%20including%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20Steve%20Jobs%2C%20and%20Oprah%20Winfrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20two%20people%20on%20it%20that%20I%20know.%20One%20is%20me.%20The%20other%20is%20Fred%20Wilson%2C%20a%20VC%20I've%20worked%20with%20for%20the%20past%2025%20years%20at%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20here%2C%20we%20had%20AI%20build%205%2C000-word%20profiles%20for%20each%20person%2C%20and%20we%20gave%20the%20AI%20a%20certain%20template%20to%20follow.%20We%20wanted%20the%20fantasy%20board%20members%20to%20be%20able%20to%20react%20to%20things%20as%20real%20board%20members%20would%2C%20with%20actual%20things%20they've%20said%20about%20how%20companies%20and%20boards%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20built%20the%20agent.%20We%20loaded%20all%20these%20profiles%20in%20and%20then%20wrote%20a%20really%20long%20instruction%20set%20about%20what%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20accomplish%20and%20what%20our%20company%20does.%20We%20also%20loaded%20materials%20from%20past%20board%20meetings%2C%20our%20quarterly%20business%20review%20decks%2C%20and%20other%20things%20that%20real%20board%20members%20would%20have%20at%20their%20disposal%20or%20in%20their%20heads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20took%20maybe%20an%20hour%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20now%20the%20fantasy%20board%20exists%2C%20and%20I%20use%20it%20as%20a%20thought%20partner.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20will%20provide%20a%20draft%20of%20a%20board%20book%20before%20sending%20it%20to%20my%20actual%20board%2C%20and%20I'll%20say%3A%20These%20are%20materials%20for%20an%20upcoming%20meeting.%20What%20do%20you%20think%20of%20them%3F%20Are%20there%20topics%20you%20would%20have%20expected%20me%20to%20cover%20that%20I%20didn't%3F%20What%20questions%20am%20I%20likely%20to%20get%20back%20from%20our%20board%3F%20In%20return%2C%20I'll%20get%20really%20useful%20commentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20we%20put%20in%20the%20instruction%20set%20is%20that%20when%20I%20ask%20the%20board%20for%20its%20opinion%2C%20very%20generically%2C%20I%20want%20it%20to%20tell%20me%20the%20consensus%20opinion%20and%20notable%20outlying%20dissent%20with%20quotes%20of%20things%20that%20the%20fantasy%20board%20members%20have%20actually%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20also%20ask%20it%20for%20help%20with%20internal%20projects.%20I'll%20say%20things%20like%3A%20Hey%2C%20I'm%20doing%20a%20presentation%20for%20our%20kickoff%20meeting%20next%20week.%20What%20do%20you%20think%20are%20the%20top%20three%20themes%20I%20should%20hit%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20fantasy%20board%20to%20give%20me%20a%20performance%20review%20for%202025.%20It%20nailed%20it.%20The%20board%20called%20out%20the%20things%20that%20I%20would%20have%20said%20are%20my%20strengths%20and%20things%20that%20I%20would%20have%20said%20are%20problems.%20I%20sent%20the%20review%20to%20my%20executive%20team%20just%20as%20an%20FYI%2C%20and%20they%20all%20came%20back%20to%20me%20and%20said%20it%20was%20pretty%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20use%20the%20fantasy%20board%20every%20day%2C%20but%20I'm%20probably%20using%20it%20at%20least%20every%20other%20week%20for%20something.%20There%20are%20two%20big%20limitations.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOne%20is%20that%20anything%20agentic%20is%20only%20as%20good%20as%20its%20inputs.%20My%20fantasy%20board%20only%20knows%20what%20I've%20told%20it%20about%20my%20business%2C%20or%20what's%20publicly%20available.%20It%20doesn't%20actually%20know%20what%20happens%20every%20day%20in%20the%20company.%20Even%20though%20I'm%20pretty%20good%20about%20feeding%20it%20information%2C%20it%20just%20doesn't%20have%20all%20the%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20limitation%20is%20that%20they're%20not%20real%20people.%20When%20you%20have%20a%20real%20board%20of%20directors%2C%20you%20have%20a%20real%20thought%20partner%20as%20a%20strategic%20advisor.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20board%20meeting%2C%20people%20are%20in%20a%20room%20together.%20They%20have%20body%20language.%20They%20have%20facial%20expressions.%20You%20can%20tell%20when%20they%20lean%20in%2C%20when%20they%20lean%20back.%20You%20can%20tell%20when%20they%20roll%20their%20eyes%20because%20they%20don't%20believe%20something%20you%20said.%20You%20can%20call%20them%20out%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20any%20AI%20agents%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20really%20careful%20not%20to%20believe%20the%20bullshit.%20They're%20predictive%2C%20and%20they're%20good%2C%20but%20not%20perfect.%20They're%20not%20human%2C%20and%20they%20miss%20a%20lot%20of%20cues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20my%20real%20board%20about%20my%20fantasy%20board%20at%20our%20last%20meeting%2C%20which%20was%20in%20November%2C%20right%20after%20we%20built%20it.%20I%20explained%20what%20it%20was%20and%20how%20I've%20been%20using%20it.%20They%20thought%20it%20was%20great.%20A%20couple%20of%20them%20asked%20me%20afterward%20how%20I%20built%20it.%20They%20asked%20for%20a%20road%20map%20and%20said%20that%20they'd%20like%20to%20do%20something%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20viewed%20the%20fantasy%20board%20the%20same%20way%20I%20do%2C%20which%20is%20that%20it's%20a%20nice%20add-on%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20augmentation%20of%20thought%20partnership%2C%20but%20that%20it's%20never%20going%20to%20be%20a%20substitute%20for%20a%20real%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-used-ai-to-build-a-fantasy-board-of-directors-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768214221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69617d02832e0ef1ead789d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-used-ai-to-build-a-fantasy-board-of-directors-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tech%20CEO%20put%20together%20a%20dream%20board%20of%20directors%20with%20AI%20representing%20famous%20leaders.%20Here's%20how%20he%20uses%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sneedleman%40businessinsider.com%20(Sarah%20E.%20Needleman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.