it%20card%20issuers%20simply%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20sustain%20profitability%20at%20a%2010%25%20rate%20cap%2C%26quot%3B%20Noto%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BConsumers%2C%20however%2C%20will%20still%20need%20access%20to%20credit.%20That%20creates%20a%20large%20void%E2%80%94one%20that%20%40SoFi%20personal%20loans%20are%20well%20positioned%20to%20fill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoto%20wrote%20that%20personal%20loans%20could%20be%20an%20alternative%20for%20consumers%20looking%20to%20address%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlso%20if%20this%20scenario%20plays%20out%2C%20underwriting%20discipline%20and%20borrower%20education%20become%20even%20more%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Noto%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20called%20for%20the%20cap%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Friday%2C%20writing%20that%20his%20administration%20would%20%26quot%3Bno%20longer%20let%20the%20American%20Public%20be%20ripped%20off%20by%20Credit%20Card%20Companies%26quot%3B%20charging%20interest%20rates%20of%2020%25%20to%2030%25%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnacting%20the%20proposed%20cap%20would%20require%20an%20act%20of%20Congress.%20Additional%20details%20about%20the%20proposed%20cap%20haven't%20been%20released%2C%20but%20it%20has%20drawn%20concern%20from%20various%20corners%20of%20the%20financial%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fackman-trump-call-cap-credit-card-interest-mistake-affordability-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Ackman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20billionaire%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Pershing%20Square%20Capital%20Management%2C%20called%20the%20decision%20a%20%26quot%3Bmistake%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20now-deleted%20X%20post%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20mistake%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20being%20able%20to%20charge%20rates%20adequate%20enough%20to%20cover%20losses%20and%20to%20earn%20an%20adequate%20return%20on%20equity%2C%20credit%20card%20lenders%20will%20cancel%20cards%20for%20millions%20of%20consumers%20who%20will%20have%20to%20turn%20to%20loan%20sharks%20for%20credit%20at%20rates%20higher%20than%20and%20on%20terms%20inferior%20to%20what%20they%20previously%20paid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20shared%20a%20separate%20X%20post%20on%20Saturday%2C%20writing%20that%20reducing%20credit%20card%20interest%20rates%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bworthy%20and%20important%26quot%3B%20goal%2C%20but%20still%20disagreed%20with%20the%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20concern%20about%20capping%20rates%20at%2010%25%20is%20that%20doing%20so%20will%20inevitably%20cause%20millions%20of%20Americans%20to%20have%20their%20cards%20cancelled%20as%20credit%20card%20companies%20lose%20the%20ability%20to%20adequately%20price%20subprime%20credit%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BConsumers%20denied%20credit%20cards%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20turn%20to%20loan%20sharks%20whose%20rates%20and%20terms%20will%20be%20vastly%20worse%20for%20borrowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20banking%20associations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20American%20Bankers%20Association%20and%20the%20Consumer%20Bankers%20Association%20%E2%80%94%20also%20criticized%20the%20proposed%20cap%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20enacted%2C%20this%20cap%20would%20only%20drive%20consumers%20toward%20less%20regulated%2C%20more%20costly%20alternatives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20the%20administration%20to%20ensure%20Americans%20have%20access%20to%20the%20credit%20they%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsofi-ceo-trump-credit-card-cap-personal-loans-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768213861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696424ba764ca5f34d2a3c3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%