%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20his%20students%20understand%20the%20basic%20market%20structures%20and%20how%20they%20translate%20to%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20purely%20free-market%20driven%20large-scale%20economy%20out%20there%2C%20just%20as%20there's%20no%20purely%20communist%20driven%20large-scale%20economy%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Ring%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20certain%20things%20that%20the%20education%20code%20expects%20them%20to%20learn%20or%20to%20understand%2C%20but%20those%20might%20just%20not%20be%20how%20things%20actually%20work%20in%20the%20real%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVOCAB%20WORD%3A%20MONOPOLY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20market%20structure%20where%20one%20company%20is%20the%20sole%20producer%20of%20a%20good%20or%20service%20without%20close%20substitutes.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20antitrust%20laws%20prohibit%20a%20single%20firm%20from%20controlling%20a%20market%20and%20restraining%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c52b42d9-dc01-4290-b0fe-0f3f5e24b535%5C%22%3EPreparing%20teachers%20for%20students'%20evolving%20views%20on%20capitalism%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20Americans%20still%20support%20capitalism%2C%20but%20the%20view%20is%20on%20the%20decline%3A%20a%20September%20Gallup%20poll%20found%20that%2054%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F694835%2Fimage-capitalism-slips.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehold%20a%20favorable%20view%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20capitalism%2C%20down%20from%2060%25%20in%202021%20and%20the%20lowest%20percentage%20Gallup%20has%20measured%20to%20date.%20The%20decline%20is%20even%20more%20pronounced%20among%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials%2C%20with%2039%25%20of%2018-%20to%2029-year-olds%20supporting%20capitalism%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiop.harvard.edu%2Fyouth-poll%2F51st-edition-fall-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20latest%20Harvard%20Youth%20Poll%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20down%20from%2045%25%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226577%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kelsey%20Moskovits%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69612b3f832e0ef1ead77b9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224382%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKelsey%20Moskovits%2C%20a%20high%20school%20teacher%20in%20Florida%2C%20said%20that%20her%20students%20have%20grown%20increasingly%20vocal%20about%20their%20opinions%20on%20capitalism%20and%20other%20economic%20systems.%3Cp%3EAgnes%20Lopez%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Business%20Insider%20asked%20readers%20to%20share%20their%20views%20on%20capitalism%20in%20an%20informal%20survey%2C%2055%25%20said%20economic%20opportunity%20in%20the%20US%20is%20unfair%20or%20very%20unfair%2C%20and%2042%25%20rated%20their%20ability%20to%20improve%20their%20financial%20situation%20through%20hard%20work%20alone%20as%20low%20or%20very%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-email-socialism-zohran-mamdani-student-debt-housing-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esouring%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esentiment%20toward%20capitalism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20states%20want%20the%20economic%20system%20to%20be%20taught%20in%20classrooms%2C%20and%20the%20shifting%20state%20standards%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20plan%20an%20effective%20curriculum.%20That's%20why%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia's%20Democracy%20and%20Capitalism%20Lab%20established%20an%20institute%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20providing%20high%20school%20social%20studies%20teachers%20with%20tools%20to%20teach%20about%20democracy%20and%20capitalism%20in%20the%20classroom%20and%20helping%20them%20better%20understand%20free%20market%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20pressing%20topic%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20democracy%20and%20capitalism%2C%20especially%20with%20everything%20that's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Jennifer%20Seiter%2C%20the%20education%20and%20outreach%20specialist%20for%20the%20lab%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20yes%2C%20it%20is%20important%20for%20teachers%20to%20teach%20these%20things%2C%20but%20when%20they're%20being%20handed%20new%20classes%20and%20new%20topics%20without%20a%20lot%20of%20support%2C%20that%20is%20where%20they're%20searching%20for%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrent%20events%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20helping%20prepare%20teachers%20to%20deliver%20comprehensive%20lessons%20on%20capitalism%2C%20Scott%20Miller%2C%20director%20of%20the%20lab%2C%20added.%20He%20raised%20the%20example%20of%20President%20Donald%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-liberation-day-prices-inflation-economy-recession-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump's%20tariff%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%20of%20outright%20saying%20that%20the%20tariffs%20are%20good%20or%20bad%20for%20the%20economy%2C%20he%20had%20the%20teachers%20at%20the%20institute%20compare%20the%20current%20policy%20to%20Alexander%20Hamilton's%20tariff%20policy.%20Doing%20so%20would%20help%20them%20better%20understand%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20capitalism%20while%20connecting%20it%20to%20the%20modern%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20talking%20about%20pedagogical%20issues%2C%20framing%20them%20and%20getting%20a%20comparative%20element%20tends%20to%20be%20much%20more%20effective%20than%20just%20being%20like%2C%20taxes%20are%20bad%2C%20tariffs%20are%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225254467c-91da-4ad3-a62f-ffbf077e2120%5C%22%3EStudents%20are%20more%20aware%20of%20economic%20conditions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBonnie%20Monteleone%2C%20an%20Ohio%20high%20school%20social%20studies%20teacher%2C%20said%20that%20the%20biggest%20difference%20she's%20noticed%20over%20her%2030%20years%20of%20teaching%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsplintered-social-media-authentic-breed-of-influencer-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20rise%20of%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20students%20are%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20fed%20stories%20that%20an%20algorithm%20has%20decided%20they%20want%20to%20hear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20kids%20who%20are%20taking%20things%20from%20podcasters%2C%20social%20influencers%2C%26quot%3B%20Monteleone%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20as%20a%20teacher%2C%20it's%20a%20challenge%20because%20sometimes%20you're%20not%20sure%20where%20they're%20coming%20from%20with%20how%20they're%20interpreting%20their%20current%20events%20and%20the%20world%20around%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20teacher%20holding%20a%20lesson%20plan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69612b9664858d02d2180fe2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWith%20more%20states%20instituting%20financial%20literacy%20requirements%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%20started%20a%20one-week%20institute%20to%20help%20high%20school%20teachers%20learn%20about%20capitalism%20and%20craft%20their%20curriculum.%3Cp%3EJesse%20Barber%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOhio%20State%20Sen.%20Steve%20Wilson%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fohiosenate.gov%2Fmembers%2Fsteve-wilson%2Fnews%2Fgovernor-signs-wilson-bill-adding-capitalism-to-high-school-financial-literacy-curriculum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esponsored%20a%202024%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20requiring%20high%20school%20classrooms%20to%20incorporate%20free%20market%20capitalism%20into%20financial%20literacy%20courses%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bcapitalism%20or%20nothing%26quot%3B%20conservative.%20He%20doesn't%20mind%20if%20classrooms%20are%20teaching%20about%20socialism%20or%20communism%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20we%20are%20a%20capitalistic%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20we're%20going%20to%20teach%20kids%20that%20are%20going%20to%20come%20out%20of%20high%20school%20and%20enter%20the%20world%20how%20to%20function%20in%20a%20capitalistic%20economy%2C%20then%20it's%20got%20to%20be%20part%20of%20financial%20literacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20if%20the%20economic%20system%20of%20the%20US%20were%20socialism%2C%20he%20would%20push%20for%20socialism%20to%20be%20taught%20in%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20teach%20whatever%20your%20financial%20system%20is.%20And%20in%20the%20United%20States%20today%2C%20whether%20people%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%20capitalism%20is%20what%20you%20have%20to%20understand%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristina%20Elson%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Capitalism%20at%20Wake%20Forest%20University%2C%20said%20that%20as%20young%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcapitalism-tiktok-america-productivity-job-mental-health-great-resignaton-antiwork-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elearn%20about%20inequality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20become%20increasingly%20interested%20in%20how%20capitalism%20can%20work%20better%20for%20more%20Americans.%20Elson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcapitalism.wfu.edu%2Fnews%2Fcapitalismbarometer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoauthored%20a%202023%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20found%20that%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Z%20have%20shown%20more%20dissatisfaction%20with%20capitalism%20than%20Gen%20X%20and%20boomers.%20It's%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20experiential%20component%20of%20their%20upbringing%20is%20very%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Elson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20not%20get%20married%20at%20the%20same%20age%20as%20older%20generations.%20They%20do%20not%20develop%20the%20same%20financial%20or%20emotional%20independence%20that%20older%20generations%20did%20at%20the%20same%20rate%20from%20their%20parents%20or%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20Elson%20said%2C%20and%20those%20factors%20influence%20how%20younger%20generations%20view%20their%20roles%20in%20the%20economy%20and%20how%20the%20economy%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVOCAB%20WORD%3A%20SOLE%20PROPRIETORSHIP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20business%20owned%20and%20run%20by%20one%20person%2C%20who%20assumes%20all%20profits%20and%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressure%20to%20teach%20to%20state%20standards%20doesn't%20apply%20as%20much%20to%20Robyn%20Iler%2C%20a%20government%20teacher%20at%20a%20private%20Christian%20school%20in%20Virginia.%20Still%2C%20she%20said%20she%20feels%20a%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20her%20students%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20dominant%20economic%20system%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elizabeth%20Mosely%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69612bcf64858d02d2180ff3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElizabeth%20Mosley%2C%20a%20North%20Carolina%20high%20school%20teacher%2C%20said%20her%20students%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20quite%20buy%26quot%3B%20that%20capitalism%20is%20the%20best%20system%20for%20Americans.%3Cp%3EJesse%20Barber%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20some%20concepts%20and%20truths%20from%20the%20Bible%20that%20fit%20in%20with%20capitalism%2C%20but%20what%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20fits%20in%20with%20human%20nature%3F%20What%20do%20we%20know%20is%20true%20about%20humans%20and%20how%20we%20make%20decisions%3F%26quot%3B%20Iler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20presents%20her%20students%20with%20various%20economic%20policy%20ideas%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20plans%20to%20raise%20taxes%20on%20the%20wealthy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20asks%20them%20if%20they%20think%20that's%20the%20best%20way%20to%20better%20society.%20Through%20those%20conversations%2C%20Iler%20said%20she%20has%20seen%20her%20students%20develop%20a%20growing%20interest%20in%20socialism%2C%20driven%20by%20their%20belief%20that%20it%20would%20promote%20greater%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Eugene%20Mach%20started%20teaching%20high%20school%20business%20classes%20about%2011%20years%20ago%20in%20Northeast%20Ohio%2C%20he%20taught%20traditional%20curricula%2C%20such%20as%20office%20skills%20management.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20he%20felt%20it%20didn't%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20his%20students%2C%20who%20came%20from%20a%20lower-income%20district.%20He%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20ways%20his%20students%20could%20make%20more%20money%2C%20so%20he%20revamped%20his%20curriculum%20to%20be%20entrepreneurship-based.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20them%20to%20be%20able%20to%20start%20a%20business%20or%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%26quot%3B%20Mach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20works%20with%20his%20students%20to%20create%20a%20business%20plan%20and%20conduct%20market%20research%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20running%20a%20successful%20business%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20helped%20students%20graduate%20from%20high%20school%20with%20their%20own%20businesses%2C%20ranging%20from%20hair%20and%20makeup%20services%20to%20landscaping.%20Mach%20recalled%20a%20student%20who%2C%20while%20living%20in%20public%20housing%20with%20his%20mom%20and%20siblings%2C%20worked%20at%20McDonald's.%20Through%20the%20school's%20entrepreneurship%20class%2C%20the%20student%20started%20an%20LLC%20with%20his%20mom%2C%20bought%20a%20duplex%2C%20and%20graduated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-orders-accidental-landlords-sell-rent-home-mortgage-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eas%20a%20landlord%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMach%20said%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20teach%20capitalism%20in%20his%20classroom%20because%20it's%20an%20economic%20system%20that%20provides%20the%20most%20opportunity%20for%20his%20students.%20His%20class%20focuses%20on%20the%20question%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20it%20that%20we%20can%20do%20to%20make%20our%20own%20situations%20better%20and%20grow%20our%20businesses%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Elizabeth%20Mosley%20said%20that%20after%20teaching%20civics%20for%20about%20a%20decade%2C%20she's%20noticed%20that%20her%20students%20are%20growing%20increasingly%20skeptical%20of%20capitalism%20and%20%26quot%3Bthey%20don't%20quite%20buy%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20should%20be%20the%20first%20choice%20for%20a%20democracy%20because%20of%20what%20they%20see%20as%20a%20focus%20on%20profits%20and%20wealth%20building%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-capitalism-socialism-economy-jobs-social-security-unemployment-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eover%20citizens'%20well-being%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20very%20intrigued%20with%20the%20notion%20of%20a%20more%20equitable%20economic%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosley%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she's%20seen%20her%20students%20express%20interest%20in%20the%20rise%20of%20political%20figures%20with%20socialist-leaning%20beliefs%20like%20Sen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%2C%20Ocasio-Cortez%2C%20and%20Mamdani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20classroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69612c8c64858d02d218101c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224584%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStudents%20in%20Moskovits'%20classroom%20have%20discovered%20new%20beliefs%20they%20held%20about%20capitalism%20and%20the%20economy%20through%20taking%20a%20political%20compass%20quiz.%3Cp%3EAgnes%20Lopez%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20look%20at%20what%20it%20would%20be%20like%20in%20America%