nce%20without%20switching%20to%20private%20browsing%20mode%2C%20forgetting%20they'd%20be%20notified.%20A%20couple%20of%20guys%20have%20called%20her%20out%20on%20it%2C%20which%20she's%20been%20able%20to%20spin%20as%20due%20diligence%20in%20modern-day%20dating.%20A%20tougher%20one%20to%20explain%20away%3A%20when%20her%20mom%20took%20a%20look%20at%20a%20potential%20suitor's%20profile%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20I%20overshare%20with%20my%20mom%2C%26quot%3B%20Statman%2C%2025%2C%20says.%20When%20the%20guy%20brought%20it%20up%2C%20she%20claimed%20she'd%20been%20browsing%20on%20her%20mom's%20phone%20for%20whatever%20reason.%20That%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20a%20lie.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20totally%20just%20my%20mom%20looking%20and%20stalking%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESnooping%20on%20an%20ex%20or%20love%20interest%20on%20social%20media%20is%20a%20tale%20as%20old%20as%20time%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20rather%2C%20as%20old%20as%20Facebook.%20Plenty%20of%20us%20have%20been%20tempted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubtle-signs-your-ex-wants-you-back-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esee%20what%20a%20former%20fling%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20up%20to%20on%20Instagram.%20But%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20those%20platforms%20don't%20rat%20you%20out%20(assuming%20your%20finger%20doesn't%20slip%20on%20the%20like%20button).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-year-in-review-spotify-wrapped-connections-data-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20is%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20a%20different%20animal%20%E2%80%94%20a%20professional%20space%2C%20focused%20on%20work%2C%20branding%2C%20and%20self-promotion.%20LinkedIn%20is%20for%20labor%2C%20not%20love.%20But%20it's%20moving%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-linkedin-got-weird-work-life-blurred-lines-of-oversharing-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20