%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-3-release-features-launch-ai-model-coding-chatgpt-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Antigravity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20paired%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-opus-4-5-ai-model-anthropic-debut-advanced-features-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClaude%20Opus%204.5%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20at%20%26quot%3Bmidlevel%20engineer%20status.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20he%20doesn't%20regret%20his%20software%20engineering%20courses%2C%20though.%20They%20taught%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bread%26quot%3B%20code%2C%20he%20said%2C%20a%20skill%20that%2C%20coupled%20with%20his%20vibe-coding%20proficiencies%2C%20keeps%20him%20from%20being%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20one%20laid%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223614%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Shah%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69602b69832e0ef1ead77292%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223826%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20future%20is%20learning%20how%20to%20read%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2023-year-old%20Ryan%20Shah.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Shah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJavanie%20Campbell%20swung%20the%20other%20way%3A%20He%20warned%20that%20over-reliance%20on%20vibe-coding%20tools%20will%20put%20your%20career%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20who%20turn%20to%20the%20LLM%20as%20the%20God%20or%20the%20expert%2C%20they%20will%20be%20replaced%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2035-year-old%20CEO%20of%20DevDaysAtWork%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Jamaica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20software%20engineers%2C%20there's%20a%20debate%20brewing%3A%20Just%20how%20bad%20will%20the%20effects%20of%20AI%20code%20editors%20be%20on%20jobs%3F%20Some%20say%20they%20will%20shrink%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-startups-impact-leaner-g