new%20drone's%20design%20differs%20significantly%20from%20that%20of%20the%20typical%20Shahed%2C%20GUR%20said%20it%20was%20being%20classified%20as%20a%20type%20of%20Geran%20because%20it%20shares%20many%20key%20components%20with%20Russian%20Shahed-like%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20a%20jet%20engine%20made%20by%20Telefly%2C%20a%20Chinese%20company%2C%20and%20a%20microcomputer%20that%20GUR%20said%20is%20modeled%20after%20Raspberry%20Pi%2C%20a%20UK-designed%20low-cost%20computer%20that%20fits%20on%20a%20small%20board.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Geran-3%2C%20a%20newer%20drone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-rumored-jet-powered-geran-iranian-shaheds-appearing-ukraine-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresembling%20Iran's%20Shahed-238%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20earlier%20reported%20by%20Ukraine%20to%20use%20a%20Telefly%20JT80%20turbojet%20engine%20that%20allows%20the%20device%20to%20fly%20at%20speeds%20of%20up%20to%20230%20miles%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGUR%20said%20the%20Telefly%20engine%20on%20the%20Geran-5%20generates%20even%20more%20thrust%2C%20but%20did%20not%20give%20specifics%20about%20the%20drone's%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20authorities%20have%20said%20that%20they've%20found%20Raspberry%20Pi%204%20computers%20on%20Russia's%20more%20commonly%20used%20Geran-2s.%20These%20drones%2C%20modeled%20after%20the%20Shahed-136%2C%20are%20Russia's%20main%20tool%20in%20the%20hundreds-strong%20waves%20bombarding%20Ukraine%20and%20require%20computers%20for%20functions%20such%20as%20transmitting%20navigation%20data%20to%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETelefly%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20Raspberry%20Pi%20Foundation%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20similar%20request%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGUR%20said%20that%20the%20Geran-5%20also%20uses%203G%20and%204G%20modems%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http